          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At iCorrect, we specialise in Apple Watch repair services across all series. Whether the fault is a damaged OLED display, cracked glass, weakened battery, charging issue, failing sensor, or a software-related malfunction, every repair is carried out by technicians trained to work on compact, highly integrated hardware. </p><p>With years of experience restoring thousands of Apple Watches, our process is built on precision, consistency, and clear communication. Every watch is fully tested before and after repair to confirm proper functionality, and all Apple Watch repairs include a <strong>2-year warranty</strong> for complete peace of mind.</p>"
